# Generated by `apm compile` from .apm/ primitives.
# `AGENTS.md` and `.github/**` outputs ARE committed: GitHub-hosted consumers
# (Copilot chat / PR, Agentic Workflows, Cloud Agents) read them directly
# from the repo with no build step. `CLAUDE.md` is only consumed by Claude
# Code, which runs locally on a developer's machine -- so we gitignore it
# and let each contributor regenerate it via `apm compile` after checkout.
# See CONTRIBUTING.md -> Recompiling agent outputs.
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
!templates/**/CLAUDE.md
!docs/src/**/CLAUDE.md
!tests/fixtures/**/CLAUDE.md
PRD.md
PRD*.md
WIP/
